ek we seen someone get bent, drag are name through the mud again...we posted logs showing this was not true...what do you guys do? Start in on the past and then try and find the next thing to bitch at us for. Sorry folks..we can not win here. I doubt you will see many in AS post here very much...like it used to be. I must say I got caught up in these boards for a lil bit lately. I will not be returning as I see most of this bitching and arguing a waste of time ( I could be playing the game instead) These boards can say what they want..I know the people in this guild and they are very kind and friendly to me..always have been,even when I wasnt a member. Some wonder how what you call the &quot;good ones&quot; stay? Well should make you think..if they are good why do they stay..maybe because all that is stated in this board is not totally the way things are. For me..these people are great and no matter what you say or try to do..I am not leaving this guild. These people are my great friends and I value them more than people I dont know and never see in this game. I have even heard of people saying that you all will boycot us from buying and selling or what have you. Well not to be a smart ass but, My friend base on this server is rather large. These people are my friends because of who I am and how I treat them on a personal everyday basis. That does not concern me. I think some here have some power and control issues? My opinion of coarse.<br>
<br>
In closing..If you see my toon in game and need a CR or some help on something..send me a tell. I will still do my best to help you. I will buy,sell and buff any and all who ask. I do not hold grudges and I am not petty in the least. I will however not be drawn into this mire of petty bickering and fighting over completely trivial things. I think we all have better things to do then sit here and be critical of others. The other point to be made is as far as flames go..it is usually the same people over and over again...please learn to forgive and move on..life is too short to be angry all the time. I leave this with clear conscience..knowing I have never trained another intentionally,have never stole a camp,and have been generally a really nice guy on this server. I have helped many here and been there for them in their time of need. I am not woried about my reputation..I have a good one thx. Even being in this guild. Best of luck in all you do!<br>
<br>
<br>
Normad Riftwalker<br>
55th Outrider<br>
